many thanks for an awesome torrent. create a new folder called garmin on sd card and place the IMG file inside it OR in the Garmin itself you will also find a folder called garmin - place this IMG file here. Go to Tools>Settings>Map. Go to Map ingo tab at bottom of map and press --> Garmin City Navigator NT 2010.31 should appear - this proves you was successful
